title: Hour 3 - NFL Week 5 Looks Interesting, CFP Expansion
itunes:title: Hour 3 - NFL Week 5 Looks Interesting, CFP Expansion
description:
Dan recaps week 4 in the NFL and talks about some of the matchups we can look forward to next week. And he takes a minute to explore the impact of expanding the College Football Playoff to 12 teams.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
